# GraphQL schema example
#directive @goModel(model: String, models: [String!]) on OBJECT
#  | INPUT_OBJECT
#  | SCALAR
#  | ENUM
#  | INTERFACE
#  | UNION
#
directive @goField(forceResolver: Boolean, name: String, omittable: Boolean) on INPUT_FIELD_DEFINITION
  | FIELD_DEFINITION

type User @key(fields: "id") {
  id: ID!
  email: String!
  first_name: String!
  last_name: String!
  full_name: String! @goField(forceResolver: true)
}

input UserInput {
  email: String!
  first_name: String!
  last_name: String!
}

type Query {
  users(first_name: String, orderByEmail: Boolean): [User!]!
}

type Mutation {
  createUser(input: UserInput!): User!
  deleteUser(id: ID!): Boolean!
}
